# systemBarsPadding  
  
Brief description  


Selectively apply additional space which matches the width/height of any system bars present on the respective edges of the screen.



## Parameters  
  
  
  
|  Name|  Summary| 
|---|---|
| enabled| Whether to apply padding using the system bars dimensions on the respective edges. Defaults to true.
  
  
